&lt;p&gt;error Line: 245 &lt;a href=&quot;https://mahout.apache.org/users/clustering/dirichlet-process-clustering.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://mahout.apache.org/users/clustering/dirichlet-process-clustering.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
